    "audio": "http://static1.squarespace.com/static/575a11a34d088e5993b6629d/t/5a2925adec212d1d08747e60/1512647122563/Dirty+Harry+Potter.mp3",
    "audio_length": 5205,
    "description_y": "<p>This week Fuzzy is joined by a plentiful panel of podcast pals, including;&nbsp;Dudi from Shaken Not Nerd, Podcasting guest professional - Mon, and Fuzzy's special lady person, Hannah.</p><p>The Panl dive headlong into a weird universe were handguns and magic combine in a shower of mystery, wonder and period-tolerable racisim. Lucky we brought along full-time Pott-Heads, Dudi and Mon to guide us, because it is a twisted pathway when we mash together 1971s Dirty Harry and 2004s Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban.&nbsp;</p><p>Thank you to everyone who voted in the Twitter Poll to select the Harry Potter movie for this episode. Even though we watched the entire series regardless, it was nice to have some common ground to start from.&nbsp;</p><p>So pack your Marauders Map and all the .44 ammo you can stuff into your tweed jacket, this one is going to be pretty..... magical. (I'll show myself out)</p><p>Mischief managed!</p><p>Make sure you check out the other WSTP? spaces on the interwebs. There are all of the things in all of the places that you need them to be.&nbsp;</p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://twitter.com/spikethepuns\">Twitter</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/whospikedthepuns/\">Facey</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/whospikedthepuns/\">Insty</a>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://whospikedthepuns.com/\">Web</a>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:whospikedthepuns@gmail.com\">Email</a>&nbsp; &nbsp;<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCZzE2kNGc_GXziTrOKaI3VQ\">YouTube</a></p><p>WSTP? is a proud member of <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.podfixnetwork.com/\">The PodFix Network</a>. Please check out the other shows in this great podcasting community.</p><p>You can find Dudie and the Shaken Not Nerd crew on <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/shakennotnerd/\">Facebook - Shaken Not Nerd</a> &amp; <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://twitter.com/ShakenNotNerd\">Twitter - Shaken Not Nerd</a></p><p>As for our lovely lady associates,&nbsp;well.... if you don't know them already, stiff!</p><p> </p><p> </p>\n\n  \n\n  \t\n      \n      \n        \n          \n            \n              <img class=\"thumb-image\" alt=\"muppet-treasure-island-52aac4a393395.png\" data-image=\"https://static1.squarespace.com/static/575a11a34d088e5993b6629d/t/5a28923e652deabe5e214bba/1512608334431/muppet-treasure-island-52aac4a393395.png\" data-image-dimensions=\"683x960\" data-image-focal-point=\"0.5,0.5\" data-load=\"false\" data-image-id=\"5a28923e652deabe5e214bba\" data-type=\"image\" src=\"https://static1.squarespace.com/static/575a11a34d088e5993b6629d/t/5a28923e652deabe5e214bba/1512608334431/muppet-treasure-island-52aac4a393395.png?format=1000w\" />",
