    "description_x": "A Geek Out Of Water is that moment when you realize you've been gushing about something you really love to people who aren't anywhere up to the level of fandom that you are.\n\nCheck out the Podcast where listeners are taken on a journey through the world of Geekdom by Australia's senseless and irresponsible version of Starsky and Hutch.\n\nJoin Daniel Tinson and Ceri Hutton as they Geek out over Video Games, Movies, TV, comics and Pop Culture sharing their unique perspectives on life in a society that is starting to warmly hug Geek culture.",
