    "description_y": "<p>The party interrogates the God of the Astral Realm while Pera, Caitlyn, and Dorro search for the second godling that was glimpsed in Capena.</p>\n\n<p>Godsfall is an original fantasy story told through the lens of a Dungeons and Dragons game in an original world of lost magic and dead gods know as Khalgun.</p>\n\n<p>The episode was written, produced, and edited by Aram Vartian. <a href=\"http://twitter.com/CarlosCrits\">Carlos Luna</a> played Pera Rivers, <a href=\"http://twitter.com/MichaelKeyWB\">Michael Key</a> played Xion Praeten, <a href=\"http://twitter.com/DorroKnott\">Doug Horn</a> played Dorro Knott, and <a href=\"http://twitter.com/Rina_Falaval\">Kelly Shaw</a> played Rina Falaval.</p>\n\n<p>To further explore the world of Khalgun and make your own arisen adventures, pick up a copy of the Godsfall Worldbook at <a href=\"http://worldbook.godsfall.com\">worldbook.godsfall.com</a>.</p>\n\n<p>Website: <a href=\"http://www.Godsfall.com\">Godsfall.com</a>\nTwitter: <a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/GodsfallDC\">GodsfallDC</a>\nInstagram: <a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/GodsfallDC\">GodsfallDC</a></p>\n\n<p><strong>Music for this episode:</strong>\nMusic for this episode:</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.audioblocks.com/stock-audio/darkness-comes-90887.html\">Darkness Comes</a> by Bruce Zimmerman\n<a href=\"http://freemusicarchive.org/music/Dexter_Britain/Creative_Commons_Volume_5/01_The_Time_To_Run_Finale\">The Time To Run</a> by Dexter Britain\n<a href=\"http://freemusicarchive.org/music/Jon_Luc_Hefferman/Production_Music_1841/Ascent\">Ascent</a> by Jon Luc Hefferman\n<a href=\"https://www.audioblocks.com/royalty-free-audio/Lowland%20Invasion\">Lowland Invasion</a> by Audioblocks\n<a href=\"http://freemusicarchive.org/music/Borrtex/Creation/Borrtex_02_Darkness\">Darkness</a> by Borrtex</p>",
