    "title_x": "Weekly Messages - Assurance",
    "image": "http://is2.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Music49/v4/77/af/ae/77afaebe-345e-cb35-95b6-391986811dc2/source/600x600bb.jpg",
    "description_x": "Come as you are! Assurance United Methodist Church is a church with one heart, and multiple locations. We are dedicated to being a diverse community who engages in service opportunities around the very communities that we work, live, and play in the Northlake/Huntersville area and West Charlotte area.",
    "language": "English",
