    "description_x": "JourneyChurch is a community of thousands of people committed to creating cultures where people can experience God and his life-transforming power. We believe that as we help people live into their God-given potential and dreams, empower people for Biblical leadership, and help people break the cycle of poverty in their lives that our dream will become a reality. We will see cities transformed, one life at a time.",
