    "description_y": "We're getting into the good stuff now...  Prayer is an awesome privilege and the more we're learning about it the more power and freedom we will have in our lives and in our church.  However, understand as we discuss today, the powerful prayer that we develop in our prayer closet comes with a cost.  The enemy will rise up against this and will do everything he can to stop it.  But press on and press in, we are the victors as we do our part.  Listen in to be challenged and encouraged to develop \"closet prayer\" and invite the presence of the power of the Holy Spirit to go with you as you journey on...",
