    "description_x": "Changed by God to make a difference for God\" is St. Augustine Anglican Church's (Columbus, OH) mission statement. Check out our website at http://staugustinesanglican.org. These sermons from the clergy at St. Augustine's are offered to help you do just that so that you can live your life fully as a human being created in God's image and to help equip you to be one of Jesus' kingdom builders.",
