    "image": "http://is2.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Music111/v4/04/65/20/04652058-5e88-2d55-8c60-100e2a172c57/source/600x600bb.jpg",
    "description_x": "In 2014, Lee Wilson had written and produced three series of a successful sitcom & sketch podcast (\"extremely high production values, and an excellent standard of writing.” - goodpodcast.com)  <br />\n<br />\nSo he quit.<br />\n<br />\nThen he tried stand up instead.  This is the story of that journey beginning with Wilson first contemplating giving it a go, through to his first steps on stage, right up to today - spoiler alert, he's still doing it.<br />\n<br />\nA beautiful, agonising, warts 'n' all audio diary of a nobody trying to do something extraordinary.",
