    "audio_length": 997,
    "description_y": "<p>The saga continues.  I&#8217;m still alive, despite not recording anything since Summer 2017.  A lot has happened, including previewing material for Edinburgh, then Edinburgh, then the post/aftermath/comedown of Edinburgh.  Okay, so it seems that everything has been focused on Edinburgh but that&#8217;s all over now and a bright new dawn is approaching&#8230; working towards Edinburgh&#8230; 2019?!</p>\n<p>Lee Wilson is back and there is no-one that is going to stop him now.</p>\n<div style=\"min-height:33px;\" class=\"really_simple_share really_simple_share_button robots-nocontent snap_nopreview\"><div class=\"really_simple_share_twitter\" style=\"width:100px;\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/share\" class=\"twitter-share-button\" data-count=\"horizontal\"  data-text=\"Ep78 &#8211; Back\" data-url=\"http://4amcab.com/2017/12/31/ep78-back/\"  data-via=\"\" data-lang=\"en\"  ></a></div><div class=\"really_simple_share_facebook_like\" style=\"width:100px;\"><div class=\"fb-like\" data-href=\"http://4amcab.com/2017/12/31/ep78-back/\" data-layout=\"button_count\" data-width=\"100\" ></div></div><div class=\"really_simple_share_digg\" style=\"width:100px;\"><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"http://widgets.digg.com/buttons.js\"></script>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"DiggThisButton DiggCompact\" href=\"http://digg.com/submit?url=http://4amcab.com/2017/12/31/ep78-back/&amp;title=Ep78 &amp;#8211; Back\"></a></div><div class=\"really_simple_share_google1\" style=\"width:80px;\"><div class=\"g-plusone\" data-size=\"medium\" data-href=\"http://4amcab.com/2017/12/31/ep78-back/\" ></div></div><div class=\"really_simple_share_pinterest\" style=\"width:90px;\"><a data-pin-config=\"beside\" href=\"https://pinterest.com/pin/create/button/\" data-pin-do=\"buttonBookmark\" ><img alt=\"Pin It\" src=\"https://assets.pinterest.com/images/pidgets/pin_it_button.png\" /></a></div></div>\n\t\t<div class=\"really_simple_share_clearfix\"></div>",
