    "audio_length": 3580,
    "description_y": "<p>If you're not a fanboy...this popcorn action flick is great. If you love DC comics and wanted this film to salvage the DCEU...we're sorry. Maybe the next one. From Affleck's and Cavil's lackluster performances to the lack of backstory for Cyborg and Flash, the movie didn't offer much other than a way of showing how Wonder Woman is the best DC property to date. The DCEU is playing catch-up with the MCU... but probably won't catch them. Marvel had more time to develop the individual backstories before the Avengers was released, where DC had to rush to get the Justice League out. </p>",
