    "description_x": "Join talk show host and guru Dale Seever, as he opens up a mystic portal to the Deep Night, a world of regrets, revelations, and rising stars. Dale explores the dark art of comedy with an eclectic lineup of guests including comedians, actors, writers, musicians, and other practitioners of strange magic. He's not real, but his guests are.  <br />",
