    "description_x": "Think Disney's just for kids? You're DEAD wrong.<br />\n<br />\nWhen the crypt doors creek and the tombstones quake, the Grim Grinning Gays and our Token Straight Girl come out for a swingin' wake.<br />\n<br />\nJoin us as we materialize weekly and begin to vocalize about Disney from an LGBTQ perspective.<br />\n<br />\nSometimes inappropriate, usually funny, always informative; this podcast will give you a chance to delve into the more adult-side of Disney (though we're all still kids at heart.)<br />\n<br />\nEvery week the Grim Grinning Gays come out to scandalize with \"Disney News with Chelle\", and \"This Week in Disney History Featuring Muggsie\"; we'll also tell you about current Disney vacation specials. Finally, we'll all sit down at the ballroom table to discuss a wide variety of Disney topics, some of which include our trips to Disneyland and Walt Disney World, tips for your next vacation, Disney movies, and whole lot more Disney!<br />\n<br />\nRemember, rest in peace the podcast's free, so hurry back we would like your company!",
