    "description_x": "Nightmare on Film Street is the horror movie podcast hosted by two horror nuts with zero credibility. Listen in every week for a candid, comedic take on the latest in horror and genre film news, reviews, and to duke out the classics in our head-to-head movie death match. Hosted by Jon (@JonOnAString), and Kim (@KimmiKillZombie). Join us, if you dare!",
