    "audio": "http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/trnsmissions/~5/XQUsKTNQMfs/TransMissionsAltMode_053.mp3",
    "audio_length": 3901,
    "description_y": "<a href=\"https://www.transmissionspodcast.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/TMAlt053.jpg\"></a>On this episode, we are joined by <a href=\"https://twitter.com/EricCrowbar\">Eric Crownover</a>. In Comics, we review the final issue of Rom Vs Transformers: Shining Armor, in Media News, the Transformers Generation 1 soundtrack restoration project is complete, and there are several announcements for 2018 shows in Conventions News. All this and much, much more on this episode of TransMissions Alt Mode!<br />\n<br />\nThis episode was edited by Cass Ordway and <a href=\"http://www.michaelordway.com/\">Michael Ordway</a> (<a href=\"https://twitter.com/minervion\">@minervion</a>). Huge thanks to Cass and Michael for their hard work!<br />\n<br />\nTake our <a href=\"http://bit.ly/trns2017survey\">Best of 2017 Year End Survey</a>! Vote for your picks for best Transformers toys and comics of 2017! Survey is open until Friday, December 15th, 2017.<br />\n<br />\nNew Contest! Win a copy of the <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5OFFV1IqGZo\">TFNation Transformers Animated Comic! </a>Tell us you favorite character from Transformers Animated and why. Reminder: Duly Appointed Supporters of TransMissions Level Patreons get 2 entries if they enter! Send us your entries via <a href=\"mailto:contest@transmissionspodcast.com\">email</a>, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/trnsmissions\">Twitter</a>, or <a href=\"http://facebook.com/trnsmissionspodcast\">Facebook</a>! Limit one entry per person. Last day to enter! Entries must be received by Friday, December 1st, 2017!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/trnstoyhax\">Patreon Contest Announcement!</a> One lucky Patreon will win a $10 Gift Certificate from <a href=\"https://toyhax.com/\">Toyhax (formerly Reprolabels)</a> every month from September 2017 - August 2018!<br />\n<br />\nWe did it! Our new monthly show TransMissions: Declassified is unlocked for Patreons! In<a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/posts/transmissions-1-11617473\"> TransMissions: Declassified</a> we'll take a deeper dive into some aspects of the Transformers multiverse. We've reached 60 Patreon supporters, so now this is a new monthly Patreon exclusive perk for all levels. But there's still work to do! If we reach 100 Patreon supporters, the new show will be available to everyone! <a href=\"http://www.transmissionspodcast.com/2017/06/declassified001/\">We've already done Episode 1, and that is available now and free for everyone</a>. Check it out and if you want to hear more, <a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/transmissions\">sign up for the Patreon!</a><br />\n<br />\nOrder our <a href=\"http://amzn.to/2ph4mqg\">TransMissions Exclusive Cover Variant of IDW's Transformers Till All Are One #1!</a><br />\n<br />\nWant some TransMissions swag? <a href=\"http://transmissionspodcast.com/shop\">Check out our new online shop, powered by Spreadshirt!</a> (<a href=\"http://patreon.com/transmissions\">Patreon</a> Supporters, <a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/posts/online-store-6890610\">you get a special shop with a 20% discount!</a>)<br />\n<br />\nLike what we're doing and want to help make our podcast even better? <a href=\"http://www.transmissionspodcast.com/support/\">Support us on Patreon or donate via Paypal!</a> If you already support us, thank you!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nShow Notes:<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n    * Intro [0:00:33]<br />\n<br />\n    * Welcome Guest Host <a href=\"https://twitter.com/EricCrowbar\">Eric Crownover</a><br />\n<br />\n    * Check out Eric's <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCA7a2ph9Pyz3DsowrjkI0Dw\">YouTube channel Nerdy Geek Talk!</a><br />\n    * Also look for him on <a href=\"http://www.tfradio.net/category/all/transformers/tgmm/\">Radio Free Cybertron's There Goes My Money!</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n    * TransMissions Declassified December Episode 4 Teaser [0:04:34]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n    * Comic Review [0:08:30]<br />\n<br />\n    * <a href=\"http://tfwiki.net/wiki/Shining_Armor_issue_5\">Rom vs Transformers: Shining Armor #5</a> Spoiler Review<br ...",
