    "image": "http://is4.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Music62/v4/80/db/22/80db2258-e337-09c7-d723-3028c48f422a/source/600x600bb.jpg",
    "description_x": "Specializing in action movies, the Everything Actioncast is your source for the latest movie, TV and video game news and information, as well as plenty of tangents and random discussions.  Also, the crew of Zach, Chris and Joe lets you know what they've been watching every week, from the latest blockbusters to TV shows to super obscure B-movies and everything in between.",
