    "website": "http://www.everythingaction.com",
    "author": "Everything Action",
    "itunes_id": 368044198,
    "title_y": "Everything Actioncast Ep 375 “Bulletproof Punisher”",
    "audio": "https://media.blubrry.com/evaction/ia601503.us.archive.org/12/items/EAcastEp375/EAcastEp375.mp3",
    "audio_length": 8011,
    "description_y": "<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-5396\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.everythingaction.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/eacthumb2.png?resize=250%2C130\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.everythingaction.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/eacthumb2.png?w=250 250w, https://i0.wp.com/www.everythingaction.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/eacthumb2.png?resize=230%2C120 230w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 250px) 100vw, 250px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" /></p>\n<p>This week on the podcast, Zach, Chris and Joe talk about the first Avengers: Infinity War trailer, Szechuan sauce, Gary Busey, The Punisher, Crisis on Earth X, Killer Donuts, John Wick: The Comic and much more.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>News: </strong>Avengers: Infinity War trailer, Jude Law cast as original Captain Marvel, MST3K and Mindhunters renewed at Netflix, Ghosted getting more episodes but possibly refocused by new showrunner, Bryan Fuller and Mike Green quit American Gods, Mulan cast for live action reboot and Ash will met KISS in a new Evil Dead crossover comic.</li>\n<li><strong>Show and Tell: </strong>Joe and Zach saw all of The Punisher and Joe started the holiday movies with A Christmas Story, <a href=\"http://www.everythingaction.com/2017/11/29/ea-commentary-bulletproof/\">Zach and Chris watched Bulletproof</a>, Chris read issue #1 of the new John Wick prequel comic and Zach also saw Savage Dog, <a href=\"http://www.everythingaction.com/2017/11/27/review-attack-killer-donuts/\">Attack of the Killer Donuts</a> and the Arrowverse crossover Crisis on Earth-X.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We want to hear your comments and feedback. Send them all to contact@everythingaction.com. Also, be sure to subscribe, rate and review us in the iTunes music store (<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/everything-action/id368044198?mt=2\">https://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/everything-action/id368044198?mt=2</a>) and follow us on twitter <a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/evaction\">@evaction</a>, Facebook (<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/everything.action\">www.facebook.com/everything.action</a>), Instagram (<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/everything.action/\">@everything.action</a>) and Tumblr (<a href=\"http://everythingaction.tumblr.com/\">everythingaction.tumblr.com</a>)</p>\n<p>If you are shopping on <a href=\"http://www.riptapparel.com\">www.riptapparel.com</a>, use code “action” at checkout for 10% off your order.</p>",
    "pub_date": "2017-12-01 22:40:30+00",
