    "description_x": "Welcome to Linked Local Network’s Internet Radio Network. LLN’s internet radio is all about Edutertainment-Podcasts that are Educational, Empowering, Inspiring and Entertaining.  Our Various hosts talk about #Health #SocialMedia #SelfDevelopment #Business #Leadership #Parenting #Recovery #marketing #Life #Green Building\nWe are all about Link Locally-Connect Globally\n\n\n\nIf you would like to be a guest on a show please email\nmedia@linkedlocalnetwork.com\n\nTo view Show Schedule and Hosts go to:\nhttp://www.linkedlocalnetwork.com/linked-local-network-radio-schedule/\n\nListen to live streaming radio on your computer, phone or tablet, or choose from our menu of pre-recorded radio programs and listen anytime.",
