    "audio_length": 7320,
    "description_y": "DUE TO TECHICAL DIFFICULTIES - OF WHICH I/WE WERE COMPLETELY POWERLESS OVER - there was NO SHOW on 11/26/2017. \n\n\n\tHowever did I have a nice Thanksgiving? Yes I did and I hope you all did as well. Considering that I have been SOBER for over 22 years, 2 months, and 28 days - is NO longer a surprize but an acceptance of a Miracle - a GIFT given to me for surrendering to the power and dominance of Alcohol. My life has been the most incredible journey since the first day of my complete sobriety.\n\n\n\tThis show explores many different aspects of addictions and recovery ideas. Listeners can participate or choose whatever they feel may work for them. We offer ONLY SUGGESTIONS and Share our very own Personal EXPERIENCE - STRENGTH & HOPE\n\n\n\tThis Sundays Special Guest VERONICA MONTINOLA - is a Master of Feng Shui and someone who has some background dealing with addictions. You might find that what she has to share may be quite enlightening and helpful - regardless of what path in life you are following. Your Journey can be enhanced with the Help and Guidence that Ms. Montinola may offer to you. We will be taking phone calls (THIS IS A LIVE BROADCAST) so feel free to call in 323-580-5755 or email your questions / comments / suggestions to me at daniel@daare.com Our show airs Sunday evenings from 7 to 9 pm CST and we are part of the Linked Local Network of SelfHelp programs offered here on Blog Talk Radio. \n\n\n\tJust remember that recovery from addictions is NO ACCIDENT - BUT A COMMITMENT TO WANTING A BETTER LIFE AND HAVING THE WILLINGNESS TO DO WHATEVER IT TAKES TO GET & STAY SOBER. You DON'T HAVE TO GO AT IT ALONE. Join US on Our Journey into Recovery and a More Wonderful Fulfilling life. Join Steve Chuck and myself as we share unpractised / unscripted CANDID Stories of Recovery from our very own Personal perspectives. We look forward to hearing from you! Listen in Sunday 12-03-2017",
