    "podcast_uuid": "e314a6dd9ab64f9096d2317870fdbee5",
    "title_x": "Omnic Lab: A Strategic Overwatch Podcast",
    "image": "http://is4.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Music117/v4/98/88/bc/9888bc24-4245-678c-59b4-e6c2f6bfdfdc/source/600x600bb.jpg",
    "description_x": "Welcome to the Omnic Lab. A podcast that focuses on the strategies inside of the game of Overwatch. We learn through trial and error in the lab, even if things get a bit crazy and blow up sometimes! We’ll brew up team composition strategies, stir in some tips to play better, and hopefully equip listeners with the instruments they need to gain a strategic edge!",
    "language": "English",
    "categories": "Hobbies | News & Politics | Other Games | Video Games | Comedy | Technology | Games & Hobbies | Podcasting",
    "website": "http://www.omniclab.com/",
    "author": "Andres Gomez & Rob May",
    "itunes_id": 1102068116,
    "title_y": "80 - Omnic Lab - Perspectives from an outsider & a parent with Susan Lyon (Jakes Mom!)",
    "audio": "http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/omniclab/~5/VWq1CCda00Y/80+-+Omnic+Lab+-+Perspectives+from+an+outsider+%26+a+parent+with+Susan+Lyon+%28Jakes+Mom%21%29.mp3",
    "audio_length": 4252,
    "description_y": "<a href=\"http://www.omniclab.com/podcast/80-ol-jakes-mom\" >\n          \n            \n              <img class=\"thumb-image\" alt=\"Omnic-Lab-YouTube-Card-80-Jakes-mom.png\" data-image=\"https://static1.squarespace.com/static/5703d3b4044262076912d676/t/5a201e6424a694adca86641a/1512054497857/Omnic-Lab-YouTube-Card-80-Jakes-mom.png\" data-image-dimensions=\"1280x720\" data-image-focal-point=\"0.5,0.5\" data-load=\"false\" data-image-id=\"5a201e6424a694adca86641a\" data-type=\"image\" src=\"https://static1.squarespace.com/static/5703d3b4044262076912d676/t/5a201e6424a694adca86641a/1512054497857/Omnic-Lab-YouTube-Card-80-Jakes-mom.png?format=1000w\" />\n            \n          \n            </a>\n          \n\n          \n\n        \n      \n      \n    \n\n  \n\n\n\n\n\n\n<p><strong>In the Lab this week Andres got a really REALLY different style interview with Susan Lyon, mother of Jake from the Houston Outlaws. We ask her about her thoughts on the video game industry as a parent, how to support her son in esports for a career, and the developing industry around the Overwatch League.</strong></p><h2><strong>News &amp; Blue Posts:</strong></h2><ul><li><p><strong>Game Night -- RECAP</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Omnic Meta: (<a href=\"http://www.omnicmeta.com/p/home.html\">Homepage</a>)</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Moira Hero Analysis <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.omnicmeta.com/2017/11/moira-hero-analysis-dark-queen-of.html\">Nov. 28, 2017</a></strong></p></li><li><p><strong>New Omnic Meta <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.patreon.com/omnicmeta\">Patreon Page</a></strong></p></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>The<a href=\"https://us.battle.net/forums/en/overwatch/topic/20759527400#post-1\"> Doomfist Mega Fix Thread</a></strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Fixed on PTR:</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Wall Slamming with a 45 degree impact as the cut-off point for registry vs sliding off.</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Rocket Punch will break things on the make that can be broken consistently</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Seismic Slam no longer cancels when you land too close to a wall.</strong></p></li><li><p><strong><a href=\"https://us.battle.net/forums/en/overwatch/topic/20759527400#post-1\">S</a>eismic Slam now \"slides\" a short distance up ramps instead of triggering immediately and Winston leap also adjusted in the same way.</strong></p></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>Things not fixed yet</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Seismic Slam bugged when you/your target is near a corner, it will sometimes not find them as a valid target. Little longer to get a fix in place.</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Ghost Punches: going through enemies instead of impacting. Partially latency related, but there working on it.</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Corner bounce: when you Punch near a corner/edge it will force you to \"bounce off\" and slide away a good distance. Working on it.</strong></p></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>Things under investigation:</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Rocket punch vs. Rocket Punch (or Charge): inconsistent interactions between hit registration on this. Both players are ideally supposed to fall down as a result.</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Aerial Seismic Slam sometimes causing grounded SS: Reports of people being in the air and triggering the grounded version.</strong></p></li></ul></li></ul></li></ul><h2><strong>Special Thanks to <a href=\"http://www.omniclab.com/sponsors/\">Diamond Sponsors</a> &amp; New Patrons:</strong></h2><ul><li><p><strong>(11/25) Chrisdaplaya, GingerSasquash, Good Apollo, GreatRootBear, Lisome, Magic, NotMuaddib, RickyTicky, Sketchy Nonsense Podcast, Silverback, &amp; TragicZac.</strong></p></li></ul><ul><li><p><strong>New Patrons this week:&nbsp;</strong><strong>Zimmy</strong>&nbsp;&amp;&nbsp;<strong>Kevin S.</strong></p></li></ul><h2><strong>Omnic Lab Links:</strong></h2><p><strong>Omnic Lab is now a Twitch Affiliate! Sub now with Twitch/Amazon Prime!<br /><a href=\"https://twitter.com/OmnicLab\">Twitter</a>,<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/omniclab\"> Facebook</a>, <a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/omniclab\">Patreon</a><br /><a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/omniclab\">Twitch</a>,<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/omniclab\"> Youtube</a>,<a href=\"http://shop.spreadshirt.com/omniclab\"> MERCH</a><br />Discord:<a href=\"http://discord.me/omniclab\"> discord.me/omniclab</a><br />Email: <a href=\"mailto:omniclabpodcast@gmail.com\">omniclabpodcast@gmail.com</a><br />Website:<a href=\"http://www.omniclab.com/\"> </a><a href=\"http://www.omniclab.com\">http://www.omniclab.com</a><br /><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/omnic-lab-podcast/id1102068116\">iTunes</a>,<a href=\"https://goo.gl/app/playmusic?ibi=com.google.PlayMusic&amp;isi=691797987&amp;ius=googleplaymusic&amp;link=https://play.google.com/music/m/I4y3phepidybxbkdmdvccdcr44m?t%3DOmnic_Lab:_A_Strategic_Overwatch_Podcast\"> Google Play Music</a>, <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/omniclab\">RSS</a><br />--&gt;<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1igC2pliVgh9Zv5x5zmd5W1gpXoXq8cvdVk2mbIfNxFg/edit?usp=sharing\">Full Extended Show Notes</a>&lt;--<br />Rob:<a href=\"https://twitter.com/notrob\"> Twitter</a>,<a href=\"http://twitch.tv/notrobmay\"> Twitch</a>, <a href=\"http://www.velenschosen.com\">Velen's Chosen Podcast</a>, <a href=\"http://conceptcraft.libsyn.com\">Concept Craft Podcast</a><br />Andres:<a href=\"https://twitter.com/IplaiGames\"> Twitter</a>,<a href=\"https://audioblender.squarespace.com/\"> audioblender.studio</a>, <a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/iplaimusic\">soundcloud</a></strong></p><p> </p><p><strong>“Don’t be a lab rat, be a scientist...see ya next week, Omnics!”</strong></p><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/omniclab/~4/akiG8sk28jk\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>",
