    "description_x": "Do you have thoughts about stuff? We sure do. Mostly Dragon Ball Z. And rape.<br />\n<br />\nMowgli and Sara are here to complain, tell disgusting stories, and offer invaluable pop culture insights. We’ll probably get some guest appearances at some point.",
