    "description_x": "We reach those who are seeking more out of life and/or have a symptom, diagnosis, or disease. We enable an improved outlook by teaching people how to maximize their mindset. We show people how to apply biblical teachings to their lives each day and that through individual study they can build a relationship with God. You're not built to be broken, you're alive to thrive.<br />\n<br />\nWe want to share the principle with you, the principle of true health. The Power that made the body, heals the body. That power doesn't need any help, it just needs no interference.<br />\n<br />\nWhen you have a heathy functioning nervous system, eat well, exercise the right way, and remove toxins from your body, you will be healthy. Dr. Baker specializes in helping people heal from health related problems. Patients come to him when they have been told that there is nothing else that can be done.  In his office everything from depression, digestive problems, migraines, cancer, heart disease, and even autoimmune diseases are getting better.",
