    "audio": "http://www.radiorotary.org/cms/podpress_trac/feed/3808/0/Rotary_12-2-17.mp3",
    "audio_length": 1457,
    "description_y": "<p><strong>Atlanta 2017 Rotary Convention, part 6 (Aired on December 2 &amp; 3, 2017)</strong><br />\nRegular hos<img class=\"wp-image-3812 alignleft\" src=\"http://radiorotary.org/cms/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/2017-12-03-Kathy-Sarah-and-Jonah-300x225.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"317\" height=\"238\" srcset=\"http://radiorotary.org/cms/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/2017-12-03-Kathy-Sarah-and-Jonah-300x225.jpeg 300w, http://radiorotary.org/cms/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/2017-12-03-Kathy-Sarah-and-Jonah-768x576.jpeg 768w, http://radiorotary.org/cms/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/2017-12-03-Kathy-Sarah-and-Jonah.jpeg 925w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 317px) 100vw, 317px\" />ts Jonah Triebwasser and Sarah O’Connell along with producer Kathy Kruger and visiting host Dave Kruger interview some of the fascinating people at the Convention about their important projects related to the goals of the Rotary Foundation.</p>\n<p>One of the many Rotary Action Groups is “Stop Mothers Dying,” a Collaborative Action in lowering Maternity Encountered Deaths (CALMED). This program helps physicians, nurses, and midwives learn to anticipate problems of childbirth. It is not just the mothers who are saved in Third World countries, since maternal deaths have been on the rise in the United States as well. Another Rotary-related group discussed is taking African women .sex workers, giving them sewing machines, and making them into entrepreneurs,  producing shirts that are sold at Rotary conventions. Although not a Rotary program per se., the Gift of Life, which supplies hope to children with heart disease through pediatric cardiology, also was represented at the Convention. For literacy, the program Books for Africa, provides donated books by the container load to nearly every nation in Africa.<br />\nLearn more:<br />\n<a href=\"https://calmedrotary.org/\">Rotary Action Group: Stop Mothers Dying</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://clubrunner.blob.core.windows.net/00000006774/en- ca/files/homepage/the-kwenuha-women-s-association-rotary-shirt/Rotary- Livingstone-Catalogue.pdf\">Rotary Shirts from Zambia</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.giftoflifeinternational.org/\">The Gift of Life</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.booksforafrica.org/\">Books for Africa</a></p>",
    "pub_date": "2017-12-08 02:49:57+00",
