    "audio_length": 1980,
    "description_y": "Dealing with our family of origin is one of our greatest as highly sensitive people. We carry the same DNA and so we are likely to feel more from them than the others around us. Add the stress of the holidays to this and the challenges of dealing with them become even greater. \n\nSo today I am back to explore this subject a bit more. It's one of the most important things to understand as a highly sensitive person whether you are estranged from them or not, you will have to deal with these dynamics of you are going to be set free and live the life you were always meant to live. \n\nSo tune in and book your free 15 minute consultation to go even deeper and pluck out what is stopping you from feeling free, loved and cherised with Kim Gilster by emailing her at TheLiberatedSensitive@gmail.com \n\nYou will be happy that you did.",
